description:
Calling all Famitsu and Super Neptunia RPG fans! We have the perfect Super Neptunia RPG weapon set for you! With the Famitsu Weapon Set, Neptune and the gang can equip Famitsu themed weapons!

The Famitsu Weapon Set includes:
• Famitsu Sword: Neptune Only
• Famitsu Blade: Noire Only
• Famitsu Axe: Blanc Only
• Famitsu Spear: Vert Only
• Famitsu Card Set: Chrome Only

*Note: Weapons are visible during battle or cutscenes.
name: Famitsu Weapon Set
